### Configuracoes Iniciais (Variaveis)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 0. Login para obter token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "contato@opticaflow.com.br",
  "senha": "11222333000181"
}

###

@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN
@empresaId = COLE_ID_EMPRESA
@filialId = COLE_ID_FILIAL
@pacientePessoaId = COLE_ID_PESSOA_PACIENTE
@profissionalOftalmologistaUsuarioId = COLE_ID_USUARIO_OFTALMOLOGISTA
@profissionalOptometristaUsuarioId = COLE_ID_USUARIO_OPTOMETRISTA
@agendaId = COLE_ID_AGENDA

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------
### AGENDA
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Criar agenda com profissional oftalmologista
POST {{baseUrl}}/agenda
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "pessoaId": "{{pacientePessoaId}}",
  "profissionalId": "{{profissionalOftalmologistaUsuarioId}}",
  "dataHora": "2026-07-01T09:30:00.000Z",
  "duracaoMin": 30,
  "status": "agendado",
  "observacao": "Primeira consulta"
}

### 2. Criar agenda com profissional optometrista
POST {{baseUrl}}/agenda
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "pessoaId": "{{pacientePessoaId}}",
  "profissionalId": "{{profissionalOptometristaUsuarioId}}",
  "dataHora": "2026-07-01T10:30:00.000Z",
  "duracaoMin": 20,
  "status": "confirmado",
  "observacao": "Retorno com optometrista"
}

### 3. Listar agendas por filial (com filtros opcionais)
GET {{baseUrl}}/agenda/filial/{{filialId}}?page=1&limit=10&search=consulta&status=agendado&profissionalId={{profissionalOftalmologistaUsuarioId}}&dataInicio=2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z&dataFim=2026-07-31T23:59:59.999Z
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Buscar agenda por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/agenda/{{agendaId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Atualizar agenda
PUT {{baseUrl}}/agenda/{{agendaId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "confirmado",
  "observacao": "Paciente confirmou presenca",
  "duracaoMin": 40
}

### 6. Teste negativo: profissional invalido (usuario sem vinculo com oftalmologista/optometrista)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agenda
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "pessoaId": "{{pacientePessoaId}}",
  "profissionalId": "COLE_ID_USUARIO_NAO_MEDICO",
  "dataHora": "2026-07-02T09:00:00.000Z",
  "duracaoMin": 20,
  "status": "agendado"
}

### 7. Deletar agenda
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/agenda/{{agendaId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
